      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 189,
      "message": "To me, both are required:\n- 'isDebugEnabled' to prevent useless evaluation of 'toscaOperation.getClass'\n- 'toscaOperation != null' to prevent NPE when trying to write to debug logs.",
